thread.title: Hundreds rally in Florida for stronger gun control laws

title: Hundreds rally in Florida for stronger gun control laws
text:
Hundreds rally in Florida for stronger gun control laws 2:31am IST - 01:09 
Hundreds gathered outside the Federal Courthouse in Fort Lauderdale on Saturday calling for stronger gun control laws following the Florida high school shooting on Wednesday that left 17 people dead. Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
